68
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:25,520
Apa?

69
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,160
Dewi ditangkap?

70
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:33,320
Ketika bintang tunggal dilahirkan,
bencana pasti akan datang.

71
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:34,520
Benarkah?

72
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:35,920
Tunggu.

73
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:40,120
Aku sudah menghitungnya.

74
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:42,040
Kau menipu semua orang.

75
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,360
Hari ini, kau pasti dipenjara.

76
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,000
Lin Cuihua.

77
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,280
Kami menerima laporan

78
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:50,600
bahwa kau menyebarkan
kepercayaan sesat.

79
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,600
Ayo ikut dengan kami.

80
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,440
Salah siapa kau terlalu bodoh.

81
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:56,960
Orang Ketiga,

82
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,800
