100
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,400
Jangan mimpi!

101
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:47,680
Kemampuanmu hanya sebatas ini saja.

102
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,080
Urusan selanjutnya,

103
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:57,000
