dia harus memberikanku jawaban
yang memuaskan.

107
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:05,960
Ibu.

108
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:07,160
Dokter bilang,

109
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:10,160
